###############################################################################
# OBJECTIVE
###############################################################################
Verify all touch targets meet 44px minimum on real devices (or emulator).
Run Lighthouse tap target audit. Document results.

###############################################################################
# TEST METHOD
###############################################################################

### 1. Automated: Lighthouse Tap Target Audit
- Run Lighthouse in mobile simulation mode
- Check "Tap targets are not sized appropriately" audit
- Target: PASS (no failing elements)

### 2. Manual: Screen-by-Screen Verification
For each screen, verify every interactive element:
- Tap with thumb (not fingertip) — comfortable?
- Adjacent targets: can you tap one without accidentally hitting another?
- Range sliders: can you drag comfortably?
- Toggle switches: easy to reach and tap?

### 3. Device Testing Matrix
Test on:
- [ ] Chrome DevTools mobile simulation (iPhone 12/13, 390x844)
- [ ] Chrome DevTools mobile simulation (iPhone SE, 375x667)
- [ ] Chrome DevTools mobile simulation (Galaxy S21, 360x800)
- [ ] Real device if available

### 4. One-Handed Reachability Test
With phone held in one hand:
- [ ] Bottom nav tabs reachable with thumb
- [ ] Primary CTAs (Execute, Build Report, Apply) in thumb zone
- [ ] Settings button (top-right) — reachable via MobileHeader action

###############################################################################
# VERIFICATION CHECKLIST
###############################################################################

### Global Components
- [ ] Button (default): ≥ 48px
- [ ] Button (sm): ≥ 44px
- [ ] Button (icon): ≥ 44x44px
- [ ] Input (default): ≥ 48px
- [ ] Switch: ≥ 44px touch area
- [ ] ThemeToggle: ≥ 44x44px (was 32px)
- [ ] Bottom nav tabs: ≥ 44px each, ≥ 8px spacing
- [ ] MobileHeader back button: ≥ 44x44px
- [ ] BottomSelectModal list items: ≥ 48px
- [ ] BottomSelectModal cancel button: ≥ 44px

### Screen-Specific
- [ ] Login: all inputs, password toggle, sign in button
- [ ] Objects: search, vehicle rows, settings icon
- [ ] Settings: all buttons, toggles, logout
- [ ] Tracking: vehicle select, event toggles, sliders, execute
- [ ] Reports: all dropdowns, date trigger, build report
- [ ] Map: settings, map controls, playback
- [ ] Object Details: tabs, event toggles, apply, dates
- [ ] Select Objects: search, checkboxes/rows, apply
- [ ] Account Security: form elements, buttons

### Spacing
- [ ] No two adjacent touch targets overlap
- [ ] Minimum 8px gap between interactive elements
- [ ] No accidental activation when targeting adjacent element

###############################################################################
# LIGHTHOUSE TAP TARGETS AUDIT
###############################################################################
Run:
  npx lighthouse http://localhost:5173 --only-categories=accessibility --output=json

Check result:
  - "tap-targets" audit: PASS/FAIL
  - Document any failing elements
  - Fix and re-run until PASS

